AcNova Smart Irrigation Farming
Overview
AcNova is a smart irrigation system designed to optimize water usage in agriculture. Using cutting-edge technology, AcNova ensures efficient water distribution based on real-time data from soil moisture sensors and weather forecasts. This system is ideal for sustainable farming practices, reducing water waste and increasing crop yield.

Features
Real-time soil moisture monitoring
Automated irrigation based on sensor data
Cloud-based dashboard for farm management
Weather data integration for irrigation adjustments
Mobile and web access
Installation
Clone this repository: git clone https://github.com/unidatech/acnova.git
Follow the setup instructions in the docs folder.
Contributing
Feel free to submit issues and pull requests. We welcome improvements and bug fixes.

